Class UserCurrent

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.UserCurrent

  • public final class UserCurrent
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Matt on 6/6/2017. Initially had static variables in ControllerUserPage and used reflection to save time having to type up and set 9 or so static variables. Later decided that it was better to set user data to separate class in model. Using reflection proved to be unnecessary and didn't really make the code cleaner...
